      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOONSIDE LEWIS (1) was a winner (17.71) at Richmond Straight two back but out of the placings last time when 6th there. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Has good speed and is aided by the cherry draw. Should bounce back. NINJA MAC (3) caught the eye when clocking a slick 19.23 over 340m at this track three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Top win three back and can measure up again. WOOLGOOLGA LASS (4) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 19.54 beating Winged Rupee. Speedy beginner who can find the front with a clean break from the middle of the draw. Can make it back-to-back wins. BLITZ (8) returns from a ten weeks layoff and must be included.",
